{
    "name": "Gaming Mouse",
    "description": "Wireless, 20000 DPI",
    "price": 85.00,
    "stockQuantity": 100
}

### Get all Products
GET {{Host}}/api/products

### Get Product by Id
GET {{Host}}/api/products/1

