### Register a new secure user
POST {{Host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "AdminUser",
    "email": "admin@marketplace.com",
    "password": "SuperSecretPassword123!"
}

### Log in to get the JWT Token
POST {{Host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@marketplace.com",
    "password": "SuperSecretPassword123!"
}